overview: Falcon Exclusive Colby Taylor, in his first movie in four years, returns to play a role that tests the limits of his versatility as an actor and performer. Getting It in the End tells the story of two brothers: one good, one evil; one battling for what's right, the other battling for what's his. Will Colby be able to outsmart his brother or will evil prevail?
title: Getting It in the End
